body_html:
the jenkins failures mostly seem to be due to some issues with APT during the setup phase of our dockerfiles, maybe something in ubuntu repositories changed? I am puzzled.
It looks like ubuntu 14.10 is still not in EOL status, either.
So I am not sure what is going on with the breakages.
